codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-choice\">choice</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Opções: <a href=\"#opt-item.monitoring-tech\">3 options</a></td></tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: #F7F7F7\"><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-space: nowrap; background-image: url(tbl_bck00.png)\" id=\"item.financial-navigation\" class=\"hierarchy\"><img src=\"tbl_spacer.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"tbl_vjoin_end.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"icon-q-coding.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: #F7F7F7; background-color: inherit\" title=\"coding\" class=\"hierarchy\"/> financial-navigation</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">What financial navigation capacity does your facility have for medication access?</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">1..1</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-choice\">choice</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Opções: <a href=\"#opt-item.financial-navigation\">2 options</a></td></tr>\r\n<tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"hierarchy\"><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/formats.html#table\" title=\"Legenda para este formato\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/> Documentação para este formato</a></td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Conjuntos de opções</b></p><a name=\"opt-item.staffing-level\"> </a><p><b>Opções de resposta para staffing-level </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">RN/MA + MD only (minimal)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">RN champion + PharmD (standard)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Full multidisciplinary team (RN, PharmD, social worker, CHW) (advanced)</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.chw-program\"> </a><p><b>Opções de resposta para chw-program </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">None (rely on family or alternative)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">High-risk patients only</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Full integration across all HF patients</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.monitoring-tech\"> </a><p><b>Opções de resposta para monitoring-tech </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Analog only (telephone, paper diary)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Dual-track (analog and digital available based on patient)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Digital primary plus remote patient monitoring (RPM)</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.financial-navigation\"> </a><p><b>Opções de resposta para financial-navigation </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Generic Bridge pathway only (low-cost generics)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Patient assistance program (PAP) pursuit plus Generic Bridge</li></ul></div>"
